    "body": "LazyReference objects were meant as a convenience to access attributes of the current store, but may increase the risk of having an inconsistent state since they are swapped and monkey-patched separately.\r\n\r\nThis commit gets rid of the LazyReference class and makes \"spack.store.store\" the only point of access for Spack's store attributes.",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
